title: Starliner saga: See photos of astronauts landing, exiting SpaceX Dragon in Florida
body: Four astronauts were all smiles Tuesday evening when they splashed down off the Florida coast on a SpaceX Dragon capsule. See photos.

title: Elon Musk congratulates SpaceX, NASA for 'excellent work' rescuing stranded astronauts
body: DOGE head and SpaceX founder Elon Musk describes his elation on 'Hannity' after two stranded astronauts returned to Earth after spending months in space.
